Missing role / ownership
- What was your specific role on the team?
- What decisions did you personally make?
- What did you do that was different from what others did?

Missing task / goal
- What was the goal or success metric?
- What constraint made this challenging?

Missing action detail
- Walk me through the exact steps you took, in order.
- Why did you choose that approach instead of another?
- What tools or methods did you use?

Missing results / impact
- What changed because of your actions?
- How did you measure success?
- Can you quantify the outcome (time saved, errors reduced, revenue, users, etc.)?

Missing reflection / learning
- What would you do differently next time?
- What did you learn that you reused later?

Too vague / too long
- What is the one sentence version of the situation?
- What is the single most important action you took?
- What is the headline result?